'''MyRevenge''', stylized '''myRevenge''', is an International multi-gaming organization headquartered in Germany. They were found in 2006 and picked up their first League of Legends squad in 2011. In addition to their League of Legends team, they also sponsor players for Counter-Strike: GO, Shootmania, Crossfire, Call of Duty 4, FIFA 13 and Smite.

